<p class="guide-intro">Cold email for agencies is a different problem than cold email for a single rep. You're managing multiple client domains, multiple sending personas, multiple target audiences — and a deliverability issue on one client's campaign can't bleed into another's. The tool that works for a solo SDR often breaks at agency scale.</p>

