<h2>The Verdict</h2>
<p>For most cold email agencies, <strong>Smartlead is the right choice</strong>. The sub-account isolation, white-label reporting, and master inbox are purpose-built for agency workflows in a way that Instantly and Lemlist are not.</p>
<p>Choose <strong>Instantly</strong> if deliverability is your primary differentiator and your clients don't care about white-label reporting. The warmup network advantage is real and measurable.</p>
<p>Choose <strong>Lemlist</strong> only if your agency specializes in high-touch, personalized enterprise outreach where the personalization features justify the trade-offs in multi-client management.</p>

